This refactor must not activate existing Contacts or send customer-facing communications merely because fields, functions, or workflows are migrated.

During audit, migration, publication and cutover:

```text
do not automatically activate existing Contacts
do not send emails to existing customer records
do not create Calls, Meetings or outreach Tasks for existing records
do not bulk-update sequence fields with workflow triggers enabled
```

Use only controlled test records for runtime validation.

