# Canonical Deal invariant

Treat the current commercial model as:

```text
one Account
→ one canonical Deal
→ many linked Contacts
```

Do not interpret this as “one open Deal” and create another Deal merely because the existing Deal is Closed, Lost, Onboarding or Renewal.

If existing code or documentation requires multiple Deals per Account, report the contradiction before implementation.

