# Email audit Task identity

A successful automatic email must create exactly one completed audit Task.

Its duplicate identity must use the available existing fields to distinguish at least:

```text
Contact
Deal
Contact Stage
Sequence Stage = Email
Sequence Step
template name
Zoho message ID, once available
```

Where existing fields support them, set:

```text
Status = Completed
Task Type = Email Sent
Sequence Managed = Yes
Blocks Sequence = No
Task Outcome = blank
```

Do not create missing fields or picklist values.

The audit Task must never:

```text
block the Contact sequence
trigger the next step through handleTaskCompletion
be interpreted as an outstanding manual action
change Contact Status back to Working after the Contact is Closed
```

