# Migration and cutover plan

Before publishing the Contact-owned functions, provide:

```text
functions to publish
workflow rules to add or rebind
old workflow rules to disable
publication order
enablement order
disablement order
rollback order
test records
expected state after each step
```

The old Deal router and new Contact router must not both control the same Contact sequence.

Do not disable the old workflow until the replacement has been published and verified.

Do not enable the replacement while the old workflow can produce duplicate activities, unless the overlap has been explicitly tested and approved.

No live workflow or function may be deleted without separate approval.

