# Existing-record migration

Do not assume existing Deal sequence values can be copied directly to Contacts.

Produce a proposed mapping for:

```text
Deal sequence state
→ Primary Contact sequence state
```

and separately identify non-primary Contacts.

Classify existing records as:

```text
safe automatic mapping
requires Activation Task
already manually handled
stopped or suppressed
ambiguous
test or duplicate record
```

Ambiguous records must not be activated automatically.

For imported or historical Contacts, the default safe result is:

```text
no customer-facing activity
```

until the owner completes an Activation Task or the user approves a migration mapping.
